{"id":"23019","name":"鏡中故我","rarity":5,"path":"Shaman","desc":"梅花將謝未謝時，她曾喜歡將這時刻封存，留於身邊。\n許多年過去，聒噪的、甜美的、各式各樣的生命誕生於她的手下，但梅花依舊如期凋落。\n許多年過去，鏡中容顏未變，但於宇宙的尺度間，她是否也只能於短短的一瞬保持鮮活?\n「既然一切難逃逝去，創造還有何意義？」\n不知沉默了多久，風吹花落，鏡中人的回答一如舊時。\n「為了有一天，不再留住梅花。」\n她輕撫冰冷的鏡面，如這樣的自語，已不知發生過多少次了。","icon":"icon/light_cone/23019.png","preview":"image/light_cone_preview/23019.png","portrait":"image/light_cone_portrait/23019.png","ranks":{"id":"23019","skill":"徹骨梅香","desc":"使裝備者擊破特攻提高#1[i]%。裝備者施放終結技後，使我方全體造成的傷害提高#2[i]%，持續#3[i]回合，並且若裝備者擊破特攻大於等於#4[i]%，則恢復1個戰技點。\n每一波開始時，我方全體立即恢復#5[f1]點能量，同類技能無法重複生效。","params":[[0.6,0.24,3,1.5,10],[0.7,0.28,3,1.5,12.5],[0.8,0.32,3,1.5,15],[0.9,0.36,3,1.5,17.5],[1,0.4,3,1.5,20]],"properties":[[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.6}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.7}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.8}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":0.9}],[{"type":"BreakDamageAddedRatioBase","value":1}]]},"promotions":{"id":"23019","values":[{"hp":{"base":48,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":24,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":24,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":105.6,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":52.8,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":52.8,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":182.4,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":91.2,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":91.2,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":259.2,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":129.6,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":129.6,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":336,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":168,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":168,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":412.8,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":206.4,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":206.4,"step":3.6}},{"hp":{"base":489.6,"step":7.2},"atk":{"base":244.8,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":244.8,"step":3.6}}],"materials":[[{"id":"2","num":5000},{"id":"113001","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":10000},{"id":"110161","num":4},{"id":"113001","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":20000},{"id":"110162","num":4},{"id":"113002","num":8}],[{"id":"2","num":50000},{"id":"110162","num":8},{"id":"113002","num":12}],[{"id":"2","num":100000},{"id":"110163","num":5},{"id":"113003","num":6}]